OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F338A1782481687
OL,3,CDriver who killed off-duty detective
OL,4,Cin crash given suspended sentence
OL,6,FA pensioner who caused the death of a
OL,7,Fpolice detective in a crash following
OL,8,Fa "tragic miscalculation" has been
OL,9,Fgiven a suspended prison sentence.
OL,11,FLaurence Green, 72, collided with
OL,12,FKaren Smith's motorcycle as she rode
OL,13,Fhome from work near Hull on 18
OL,14,FDecember 2024.
OL,16,FGrimsby Crown Court heard he failed to
OL,17,Frealise how close she was before
OL,18,Fpulling out of a junction on Thorn
OL,19,FRoad, Hedon,
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,339,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F338A1782481687
OL,3,CDriver who killed off-duty detective
OL,4,Cin crash given suspended sentence
OL,6,FJudge Gurdial Singh told Green: "You
OL,7,Fmade a tragic miscalculation and
OL,8,Fallowed insufficient time to complete
OL,9,Fthe manoeuvre, causing the collision.
OL,11,F"It was entirely your fault. This was
OL,12,Fnot an intentional act on your part. I
OL,13,Fdo accept that your remorse is
OL,14,Fentirely genuine."
OL,16,FGreen, of Littleham Close, Bransholme,
OL,17,FHull, admitted causing death by
OL,18,Fcareless driving.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,339,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F338A1782481687
OL,3,CDriver who killed off-duty detective
OL,4,Cin crash given suspended sentence
OL,6,FHe was given a one-year suspended
OL,7,Fprison sentence and he was banned from
OL,8,Fdriving for two years.
OL,10,FJeremy Evans, prosecuting, told the
OL,11,Fcourt Green was driving a Honda
OL,12,FInsight and had his partner in the car
OL,13,Fwhen the incident happened shortly
OL,14,Fafter 5pm.
OL,16,FDet Con Smith, aged 49 and a mother of
OL,17,Ftwo, died at the scene.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,339,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F338A1782481687
OL,3,CDriver who killed off-duty detective
OL,4,Cin crash given suspended sentence
OL,6,FMr Evans said: "The defendant failed
OL,7,Fto give way to the approaching
OL,8,Fmotorcycle and turned into its path.
OL,9,FHe was apologetic about the whole
OL,10,Fincident."
OL,12,FGreen said at the scene: "I didn't see
OL,13,Fthem. They came out of nowhere. I
OL,14,Fwasn't going fast. I am so sorry."
OL,16,FGlenn Parsons, mitigating, said: "He
OL,17,Fsends out deep remorse to the family,
OL,18,Ffriends and colleagues of Karen Smith.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,339,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F338A1782481687
OL,3,CDriver who killed off-duty detective
OL,4,Cin crash given suspended sentence
OL,6,F"Never in his wildest nightmares would
OL,7,Fhe imagine that he would be in court,
OL,8,Flet alone in a case where someone has
OL,9,Flost their life. He does not intend
OL,10,Fever to drive again.
OL,12,FHe described the incident as "a
OL,13,Fterrible error of judgement".
OL,15,FFollowing the the incident, Humberside
OL,16,FPolice Federation described the
OL,17,Fdetective as a "well-liked and popular
OL,18,Fcolleague".
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
