CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F338A1782481687
OL,3,CDriver who killed off-duty detective
OL,4,Cin crash given suspended sentence
OL,6,FIt added: "She showed an incredible
OL,7,Flevel of compassion for victims of
OL,8,Fcrime and tirelessly pursued justice
OL,9,Ffor them.
OL,11,F"These attributes made her stand out
OL,12,Fas a truly outstanding detective."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/6
